            "review_text": "I grew up watching my father play the sid meier's games, chief amongst them were civ III and pirates.  i have loved being able to play these classic gems throughout my childhood and into adulthood. However as of recent Civ III runs about as well as a crippled horse through a mine field. constantly freezing and kicking me out of the application entirely. i recommend people buy / play civ V as it is more recent and not as prone to freezing \r\n"
